name: Complex visions
description: Digital combination of two of my own analog paintings of faces, further painted and developped digitally. The work reflects on how new visions, insights and realizations have a transformative power both towards inside and outside. Previously stable structures and concepts can become fluid or disintegrate, ideas of self can shift and transform, new deeper seeings can open up. The complexity of transformation is that it can both be painful and liberating at the same time.
